Interface TreeNode

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    MutableTreeNode
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MutableTreeNodeImpl

    public interface TreeNode
    Defines the requirements for an object that can be used as a node in the TreeNodeTreeModel class.
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)
